rows.label: xs33200120_MSG0050
rows.name:
"Here lies he, the one endowed with the foremost intellect...
since time and space began...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200120_MSG0060
rows.name:
"This one was fellow to the Samaar,
yet also bringer of unbridled calamity.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200120_MSG0070
rows.name:
"This one is deserving of punishment.
Yet, death as penalty is to us anathema.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200120_MSG0080
rows.name:
"Intellectual atrophy via endless incarceration—
a prison of the mind is meet for he."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200120_MSG0100
rows.name: They must be talking about Void.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200120_MSG0120
rows.name: it must've been his prison, no doubt about it.[ST:wait ]
